%N A393518 Number of unlabeled rooted trees with n nodes whose level sizes are equal, excluding the root level.
%C A393518 Level size is the number of nodes (terminal or nonterminal) at a given distance from the root.
%C A393518 a(n) = 2 where n-1 is prime.
%C A393518 Open question: Does the sequence contain any value greater than 2 more than once?
